<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Surely it is in vain that I have guarded my heart</para>

<para style="q1">and washed my hands in innocence.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />For all the day long I have been afflicted</para>

<para style="q1">and disciplined every morning.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />If I had said, "I will say these things,"</para>

<para style="q1">then I would have betrayed this generation of your children.</para>
